Subject:  cp and copying directories
Index: 	bin/cp 4.2BSD

Description:
	When cp copies a directory without the -r option, the directory
	loses its directory attribute and no warning/error message is
	generated by cp.
Repeat-By:
	mkdir testdir
	cp testdir <anydir>
